This project contains derivative works and modifications based on multiple open source projects:

================================================================================
EPYMARL-BASED CODE (marl_mrt2a/marl/)
================================================================================

The code in marl_mrt2a/marl/ is based on EPyMARL (Extended Python MARL framework):
- Original EPyMARL: https://github.com/uoe-agents/epymarl
- EPyMARL License: Apache License 2.0
- EPyMARL is itself based on PyMARL: https://github.com/oxwhirl/pymarl
- PyMARL License: Apache License 2.0

Modifications made to EPyMARL by Lucas C. D. Bezerra (2025):
- Integration with `gymrt2a` environment
- Addition of CNN-based agents and critics for spatial environments
- Custom action selection and filtering for grid-based tasks
- Multi-dimensional action, observation, and state spaces
- Spatial action interfaces and intention sharing mechanisms

